<!doctype html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    class="bg-light min-vh-100"
    style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e0f7fa, #ffffff)"
  >
    <header class="container py-4">
      <nav class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <img
          src="/img/Hakobun_icon.png"
          alt="Hakobun Logo"
          width="80"
          height="80"
        />
        <button class="btn btn-info text-white">ログイン</button>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container py-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary mb-3">
          Hakobun で簡単にお土産を代行してもらおう
        </h1>
        <p class="lead text-secondary mb-4">旅行のお土産で誰かの助けに</p>
        <button class="btn btn-info btn-lg text-white px-4 py-2">
          使ってみる <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="bi bi-box text-info fs-1 mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold">魅力をかく①</h3>
              <p class="card-text text-secondary">○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○します。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="bi bi-geo-alt text-info fs-1 mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold">魅力をかく②</h3>
              <p class="card-text text-secondary">○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○します。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0 bg-white">
            <div class="card-body">
              <i class="bi bi-truck text-info fs-1 mb-3"></i>
              <h3 class="card-title h5 fw-bold">魅力をかく③</h3>
              <p class="card-text text-secondary">○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○○します。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 bg-white mb-5">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-center h3 fw-bold mb-4">お客様の声</h2>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0">
              <div class="border-start border-info border-4 ps-3">
                <p class="fst-italic mb-2">
                  「Hakobunのおかげで、とても便利です！」
                </p>
                <p class="text-secondary">- 田中さん、東京</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <div class="border-start border-info border-4 ps-3">
                <p class="fst-italic mb-2">「「良いサービスでした。」</p>
                <p class="text-secondary">- 阿部さん、大阪</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white py-4 mt-5">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2024 Hakobun. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
